tmpfile/mkstemp:Potential for temporary file vulnerability in some circumstances. tmpfile/mkstemp:Potential for temporary file vulnerability in some circumstances.  Some older Unix-like systems create temp files with permission to write by all by default, so be sure to set the umask to override this.
